# ==============================
# 🤖 Models / Checkpoints
# WHY models are NOT pushed to git:
#   - .pth files are hundreds of MB → bloats repo, breaks GitHub push limits
#   - Git is for code, not binary weights
#   - Models are downloaded at Docker BUILD TIME from HuggingFace
#   - Use HuggingFace Hub or cloud storage for model distribution
# ==============================

# ❌ Ignore ALL model formats everywhere
*.pth
*.pt
*.onnx
*.ckpt
*.bin
*.safetensors

# ❌ Ignore all model directories
models/*
ai/models/*
backend/models/*

# ✅ Keep the directories themselves (so git tracks the folder structure)
!models/.gitkeep
!ai/models/.gitkeep
!backend/models/.gitkeep

